STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Curt Douglas STEFFEN, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1959 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A defendant challenges his conviction for second-offense operating while intoxicated. DISTRICT COURT JUDGMENT REVERSED IN PART AND CASE REMANDED.

DISTRICT COURT JUDGMENT REVERSED IN PART AND CASE REMANDED.
